items.name: Canon MF212w Mono MFP Wireless Laser Multifunctional Printer/Copier/Scanner
items.shortDescription: The Canon MF212w Mono MFP Laser Multifunction Printer is an easy-to-use, wireless unit that produces professional output and features an array of mobile capabilities. With print, copy and scan needs combined into one compact device, your small office or home office will run efficiently. For simple mobile device printing, you can use Apple AirPrint, which allows you to print wirelessly from Apple iPad and iPhone. The Mopria Print Service is available for your mobile printing needs as well on an Android phone or tablet (Android version 4.4). With Canon Mobile Scanning for Business, you can easily scan documents from your MF212w to your iOS or Android mobile device and have them ready for your distribution or backup needs wherever you are. It's simple to stay productive in your small or home office with features like a Quick First Print of six seconds and fast print speeds of up to 24 pages per minute on the Canon MF212w Mono MFP Laser Multifunction Printer.

items.name: RCA 7" Tablet 16GB Quad Core.
items.shortDescription: <p>Introducing the RCA 7 Voyager II 7-inch Google Certified Tablet. Operating on Android's sweetest operating system yet, Android 5.0 (Lollipop), you can enjoy more of what the Google Play store has to offer, whether you're into gaming, social apps, music, movies or are looking for the latest productivity app. Share a smile with friends and family using the tablet's front camera. Use the tablet's built-in Bluetooth capability to connect and pair with compatible devices. Whether taking in a movie, playing a favorite game or surfing the Web, the RCA tablet's quad-core processor and 16GB flash-storage provide an excellent portable experience.</p>
items.longDescription: <b>RCA 7 Voyager II with WiFi 7" Touchscreen Tablet PC:</b><br><br><b>Technical Specifications:</b><br><br><ul><li>1.3GHz Quad-Core processor</li><li>1GB DDR of system memory</li><li>7.0" touchscreen, 1024 x 600 resolution</li><li>Built-in WiFi and Bluetooth v4.0</li></ul><b>Additional Features:</b><ul><li>Front 1MP webcam</li><li>microUSB 2.0 port, headphone jack, microphone jack</li><li>16GB onboard storage memory, additional memory via microSD card slot</li><li>Rechargeable lithium-ion battery</li><li>Weighs 0.61 lbs; 7.3" x 0.5" x 4.5" dimensions</li></ul><b>Software and Applications:</b><ul><li>Android 5.0 OS (Lollipop)</li><li>Media Formats: popular media formats</li></ul><b>What's in the Box:</b><ul><li>Tablet, battery and AC adapter</li></ul><br><b>What's a Tablet PC?</b><br><br>Tablet PCs are compact, ultra-portable entertainment devices that let you read email, surf the Internet, read eBooks, view photos, play games, listen to music and watch video files. Tablet PCs do not have a CD/DVD drive and will not run Microsoft Windows or its applications. Tablet PCs function as a secondary device for casual entertainment purposes, and are not meant to replace a computer. items.name: EPIK Learning Tab 7" Kids Tablet 16GB Intel Atom Processor Preloaded with Learning Apps & Games
items.shortDescription: The EPIK Learning Intel Quad Core 7" Kids' Tablet brings your child a compact, ultra-portable entertainment device that will let them read email, surf the Internet, read ebooks, view photos, play games, listen to music and watch video files. The tablets are based on a smaller operating system, which allows you to purchase and download additional applications from supported stores for your child to enjoy. They do not have a CD/DVD drive and will not run Microsoft Windows or its applications. They function as a secondary device for casual entertainment purposes and are not meant to replace a computer. The kids' learning tablet is ideal for use around the home and on the go with WiFi or 3G to 4G mobile broadband connections, although a pay-as-you-go contract may be required for service.
items.longDescription: EPIK Learning has partnered with Intel, a worldwide leader in computing innovation, to deliver an exciting tablet experience for kids and parents. This device is a truly smooth all-in-one solution for education and fun. It is preloaded with award-winning mobile apps for children and adults, such as Looney Tunes Phonics, SmartRunner Series, ClickN Spell, Google Play and much more. The EPIK Learning Tab boasts DPI (Dual-Purpose Interface) technology, which allows both parents and kids to enjoy this full-featured tablet. The 16GB tablet provides plenty of storage for all of the entertaining and learning apps your child will want to use. They come in a bright arrangement of colors, allowing you to choose your little one's favorite look. The system offers up to five hours at a time on a full charge, giving lots of time for play. It comes with a battery, gel case and AC adapter, so your child can start using it right away.
